column1: # Fields for custom shapes contain number of vertices, and vertex position in the form of (X:Y:Z) for CUSTOM3D or (X:Y) for CUSTOM2D relative to center of screen
# CUSTOM3D/2D Args: [Stroke Color], [Fill Color], [Optional: beginShape param] [No. of Verts N], [Vert1] [Vert2] …. [VertN] [Optional: Contour,etc, [No.of Verts N], [Vert1], [Vert2]…[VertN]]
# SPHERE Args: [Stroke Color], [Fill Color], [Diameter], [positionX], [positionY], [Animation (to be implemented)]
